      • addChild

        public void addChild(IFXGNode child,
            Collection<ICompilerProblem> problems)
        Adds an FXG child node to this Graphic node. Supported child nodes include graphic content nodes (e.g. Group, BitmapGraphic, Ellipse, Line, Path, Rect, TextGraphic), control nodes (e.g. Library, Private), or property nodes (e.g. mask).

        Overrides:
